description: Within our own universe lies another universe unbeknownst to us... until now. The realm of the MICRONAUTS - a place ruled by evil tyrant, Baron Karza, whose scientific marvels offer his people immortality, at the cost of their humanity. When unsuspecting, Ryan Archer is thrown into their world, we find that not only are things about to change, but Ryan will have much to do with it.Â  Meet Persephone. In a fantastic, cold and metallic, science fiction landscape, she's the most beautiful woman stranded and incarcerated Earthman Ryan Archer has ever laid eyes upon. But is she friend or foe? Meanwhile, we learn from the warrior Acroyear, the details of Baron Karza's malicious rise to power and how he became the powermad dictator that he is. It's not a pretty story.
name: Revolution (Part 2)

But how could this irresponsible Earthman with no fighting skills possibly contribute to their cause? Meanwhile, what do the mindless killing machine Biotron and the probe droid called The Micronaut have in common? The answer may surprise you.
name: Revolution (Part 3)

description: Within our own universe lies another universe unbeknownst to us... until now. When unsuspecting, Ryan Archer is thrown into their world, we find that not only are things about to change, but Ryan will have much to do with it. The action heats up as Ryan and Koriah, the Galactic Defender, meet up with a band of infiltrating revolutionaries intent on helping them escape Baron Karza's iron grip. Besieged by a troop of Harriers, the group is forced under the streets of echopolis where they make a shocking discovery! Meanwhile, Acroyear and Knave, released from the IsoPen by an unknown benefactor, are discovered and forced to fight for their lives. And what does the inert Micronaut probe have to do with the resuscitation of the deadly automaton called Biotron?
name: Revolution (Part 4)

When unsuspecting, Ryan Archer is thrown into their world, we find that not only are things about to change, but Ryan will have much to do with it.Â  The stunning finale to REVOLUTION! Loyalties and allegiances are tested as Baron Karza's control over his city of Mechopolis falters. Ryan, Koriah the Galactic Defender and the band of revolutionaries make their final bid for escape. Acroyear once again squares off against General Azura Nova, a battle which one of them won't walk away from unscathed. Knave shakes the cobwebs off of a long forgotten talent in order to stay alive. The Princess Perspehone makes a big mistake. Biotron harbors a secret. And Karza himself makes an appearance on the battlefield. Don't miss the action-packed conclusion to the story that sets the stage for the future of the Micronauts!
name: Revolution (Part 5)

Hurtling across space and pursued by what seems like every bounty hunter in the galaxy, the 'Nauts make their way to a backwater planet. But will facing danger tear the already fragile alliance of the Micronauts apart? Meanwhile, Karza plots his biggest conquest ever...

When unsuspecting, Ryan Archer is thrown into their world, we find that not only are things about to change, but Ryan will have much to do with it.Â  Having defeated the bounty hunter Ordaal and taken his ship, the Sunreaver, the Micronauts try to rendezvous with a contact that will tell them what Baron Karza's next move is. What they actually meet in the depths of outer space, however, stuns them all... Featuring the judgement of Azura Nova and a shocking visitation by a Time Traveler, the Micronauts' saga continues in "Star Chamber."
name: Star Chamber

description: Ryan Archer returns to Earth with his Micronauts companions to find his world locked in a massive war with the forces of Baron Karza. Steve Kurth of KARZA joins the series as new penciller! The invasion of Earth is already well underway, as the Micronauts discover first-hand when they arrive in the middle of a massive aerial battle. Things quickly go from bad to worse as Baron Karza launches his plan of global enslavement and genocide-and the winged fighter called Red Falcon zeroes in on the 'Nauts to deal some personal damage. It's a lousy day to be human, in "Welcome to Earth."
name: Welcome To Earth

description: In a society where technological advancement is its only aspiration, the human factor is considered nothing more than a small part of an equation. But Radix changed all that. Follow Valerie Fiores, as she takes the journey to discover the truth about herself, her past, her world, and about -- Radix. On a planet called Earth, scientists discover a mysterious force. It's thought that it would lead the human race to a new era. Six major cities throughout the globe combined their efforts in hope to understand it. However, the force grew out of control and five cities where left annihilated in its wake. Now time is running out for the remaining one. They must find a way to contain it before suffering the same fate. The dawn of a new era in evolution -- Radix.

name: Old Ghosts and, New Blood ... part 1
Old Ghosts and, New Blood ... part 2

description: Ryan Archer returns to Earth with his Micronauts companions to find his world locked in a massive war with the forces of Baron Karza.Â  With Karza's Earth invasion well under way and the team splintered and lost, it's up to Ryan Archer to re-unite them. And all he'll have to do to accomplish that is deal with Karza's genocide machines, the fearsome winged warrior called Red Falcon, his own body's mysterious molecular flux, and... his ex-girlfriend. It's wall-to-wall action and intrigue as "Invasion" continues.
name: Invasion (Part 1)

description: Â Ryan Archer returns to Earth with his Micronauts companions to find his world locked in a massive war with the forces of Baron Karza.Â  It's down to the wire now: with Baron Karza moments away from carrying out his plan of global genocide, only the Micronauts stand between him and the conquest of the entire Earth dimension. And yet, with Ryan Archer's body on the verge of disintegrating and the vicious Red Falcon out for the team's blood, can they even get to Karza's new citadel in time? See whether or not Earth itself survives as "Invasion" draws to a close.
name: Invasion (Part 3)

description: His name is Shobu, ordinary kid and Duel Master tournament champion. Thanks to his mysterious and missing father, Shobu has an unexpected edge in the card games, for he alone can directly access the "Zone," a dimensional realm where mythical and mystical battles are fought between wild beings to the finish. Plenty of would-be masters want to challenge Shobu and even stranger beings want his access to the Zone, but for now the champ stands tough. But a quest for his missing father will open even stranger and deeper mysteries than the boy could have expected.
name: Duel Masters

description: The mystery of battle zone and the realm beyond deepens, as Shobu and friends enter a major Duel Masters tournament for the first time. The search for Shobu's missing father leads to an astonishing revelation?which points to ever deeper secrets and wild and constant danger! Can Shobu breach the vast gulf between worlds in order to save his dad? Will the senior Kirifuda survive long enough for the puzzle to be unraveled?. The search for Shobu's missing father leads to some very strange places. Â

Shobu begins to understand what it means to truly be a Duel Master as the significance of his special abilities become more evident. But with his gifts and mastery of the game, he still has no idea what ever became of his father. Nor does he grasp what his visions of a terrifying other realm of fire and fear really mean. Somewhere in all of the scary possibilities lie the answers he seeks, if Shobu is brave enough to face them.Â
name: When Worlds Collide

description: Believed to be the embodiment of an ancient Incan prophecy, and exiled years earlier for abusing her own powers, Rayne Santiago must confront the past she has been running from her entire life if she hopes to not only win back the trust of her people, but also rescue her brothers.

Set between the first and second games of the Maximo franchise.Â 
Maximo is called to save a kingdom from evil. He must defeat the demon lord Skaab and his plague of decaying demons known as The Rot.

A convent in Spain. Nuns going about their routine in the name of God. But all is not quite as it seems. There are cracks on the surface. Some nuns seem to harbor secret lusts for each other. Then's there's an accident in the cellar revealing a very old condemned door found on no plan. One of the less holy nuns has a satanic nightmare about it. She decides to find out. What she unleashes is an unholy bedlam of depravity and lust! Beautifully painted and full of very raw sexual energy!
